    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "meditation isnt gonna stop my nerves from screaming. i've tried the breathing, the mindfulness, all that stuff... it just makes me more aware of how much i'm hurting because i'm forced to sit still with it. it feels like i'm just putting a tiny bandage on a gaping wound. honestly, i don't want \"calm\" while i'm still suffering. i just want it to stop. it feels like the only real way to get that peace is to just... stop being. is that so wrong to think? to just want a merciful end to all this?",
